results.name: Numerators of Blandin-Diaz compositional Bernoulli numbers (B^sin)_3,n.
comment: Denominators are A132093. Numerators and denominators given only for even n (odd n have numerators = 0).
reference: J. Riordan, Combinatorial Identities, Wiley, 1968, p. 199. See Table 3.3.
link: Hector Blandin and Rafael Diaz, Compositional Bernoulli numbers, arXiv:0708.0809 [math.CO], 2007-2008, see p. 8.
maple: A132092 := proc(n) local g; g := taylor(sin(x)-x,x=0,n+7) ; g := taylor(g/x^3,x=0,n+4) ; g := taylor( 1/6/g,x=0,n+4) ; n!*coeftayl(g,x=0,n) ; numer(%) ; end: for n from 0 to 40 by 2 do printf("%d,",A132092(n)) ; od: # _R. J. Mathar_, May 25 2008
mathematica: ((x^3)/3!)/(Sin[x]-x) + O[x]^(2m) // CoefficientList[#, x]& // #*Range[0, 2m-2]!& // #[[;; ;; 2]]& // Numerator (* _Jean-François Alcover_, Mar 23 2020 *)
